      <scopecontent id="aspace_178d5d2059c3922f4a5b15bed20a8d34">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection comprises eight volumes of designs for the painting of Worcester porcelain and one account book, the work of Henry Taylor (1825-1888), his father James Taylor (1790-1852), and his grandfather William Taylor.</p>
      </scopecontent>
